	<div style="text-align:right;">
		WAKASSUGUI, Caroline Pimenta Martins<sup>1</sup>; TEIXEIRA, Elenice Cacia Bittencourt<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
